{"tid":1267332,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"十二分鐘話你知香港警賊無學識、弱智兼戇鳩","createTime":"2019-06-29T20:57:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-29T23:33:40.000Z","uid":138212,"like":29,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6b0f0ece9326e9dd2fd2228634b0a143d62fa2ba","tid":1267332,"uid":138212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T20:57:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/100002711881371/videos/1934268526673525/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F100002711881371%2Fvideos%2F1934268526673525%2F&d=FGEw0iwwiNltpS2R1LMyGh5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=ff747a72\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/100002711881371/videos/1934268526673525/</a><br />\n事主夜晚想用架共享單車返屋企，掃完個qr code先知間公司執左<br />\n呢個時候三四隻警犬以為事主想偷單車走埋黎搜身<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">睇到一半你會知班原來警犬係完全唔撚知咩係共享單車，仲要以為qr code係一個app</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不停插嘴果隻警賊仲要聲大夾惡，自己講唔到道理又係咁重複人地講野，小學雞咁，仲好意思話呢道我話事，黑社會咩<br />\n仲話手指指唔講粗口就唔係無禮拜？我同你講每日趁你當更同你老婆老母3p咁算唔算有禮貌呀呀sir<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後發覺講唔贏又柒左先氣沖沖叫個伙記拎cam影返個後生仔，到最後咪又係要放人<br />\n<br />\n分享畀各位手足除左笑鳩差佬其實要學事主咁遇到警犬無理搜身要即刻開cam影撚實，保障自己之餘日後投訴都方便D<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49e3a42664d098e0909fae95ed1395e0e32c21d0","tid":1267332,"uid":86756,"like":3,"dislike":21,"score":-18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T21:07:58.000Z","msg":"警察認為有懷疑去查袋的，事主唔合作"},{"pid":"eb54c29889f78c0980de5b9eb76a2522e42718a3","tid":1267332,"uid":62025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T21:19:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f941a443a74a5867fbb90302aaa7ab1ba787870","tid":1267332,"uid":62025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eb54c29889f78c0980de5b9eb76a2522e42718a3","tid":1267332,"uid":62025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T21:19:52.